The paper discusses the theory behind deep learning and how deep neural networks can efficiently perform hierarchical learning. This topic is closely related to machine learning (cs.LG), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), neural networks (cs.NE), computer vision (cs.CV), and data structures (cs.DS). Therefore, these are the most likely arXiv CS sub-categories for this paper, ordered from most to least likely.
